{"tid":426760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當會員comment post都可以借到位連登仔屌，你就知某部分會員有幾反智","createTime":"2017-10-07T02:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T04:47:16.000Z","uid":23170,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18e560fcc95fa3850ed26a0c26cc364850bf3dee","tid":426760,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:39:35.000Z","msg":"你屌肥絲嫌佢改字煩，我明。<br />\n<br />\n但係你屌一個正常會員，只係因為佢留言次數過密係乜玩法，一個討論區可以屌一個人過份參與討論！？大佬呀，你開個討論區做乜呀？做cdrom!? 你唔抵得人咩嘢都討論到自己就成個毒撚咁連comment都唔敢comment!? 5p雜交你唔屌，投正負評post你唔屌，但你走去屌一個正正常常嘅會員！？？？你想連登係有個正常討論氣氛嘅地方，就唔好連一個人comment都屌啦，用下你個死人腦先屌啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps, 龜頭小嘴會員要走只可以證明你地班仆街反智到乜嘢地步！"},{"pid":"daa51a28a444560c808e468eff0d68c1efd67153","tid":426760,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"你地班仆街實駁唔到，因為成件事根本就弱智無理性可言。隨便負皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9df272851cf3ae2763f5ac6cd3cba2e15c29d9","tid":426760,"uid":20584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"你都識講係「正常討論既地方」<br />\n慘在佢留言全部都係唔係關於個討論呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3b0bfcae83efa2a6a7cba24897d9fb86d7e365","tid":426760,"uid":117237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地班仆街實駁唔到，因為成件事根本就弱智無理性可言。隨便負皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n55<br />\n大家留負皮就走啦"},{"pid":"0573380bf8c79486b16417a82b413db88a4ad9cb","tid":426760,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都識講係「正常討論既地方」<br />\n慘在佢留言全部都係唔係關於個討論呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我夠見到佢comment, 次次我只係見到佢順住主題comment㗎，有無好似肥絲咁騎劫晒成個post!? 無呀。一個好人好者嘅會員俾你地咁老屈真心好嬲睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a10e37a2b65d781797cf3d260926e38b945493","tid":426760,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你都識講係「正常討論既地方」<br />\n慘在佢留言全部都係唔係關於個討論呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我夠見到佢comment, 次次我只係見到佢順住主題comment㗎，有無好似肥絲咁騎劫晒成個post!? 無呀。一個好人好者嘅會員俾你地咁老屈真心好嬲睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有你唔好搵感情台啲假膠post做例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be93bd6352c30bf27b42bf2b5474f6974292d253","tid":426760,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地班仆街實駁唔到，因為成件事根本就弱智無理性可言。隨便負皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n55<br />\n大家留負皮就走啦</blockquote><br />\n幾叻呀，以前舊登啲人會識駁識拗，依家連登仔最勁就係留負皮。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你睇下我個負皮留得幾有說服力</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcc9bff4775241a09601375ef6b48703744a08d","tid":426760,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都識講係「正常討論既地方」<br />\n慘在佢留言全部都係唔係關於個討論呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n例子一：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/420968/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/420968/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n例子二：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/382124/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/382124/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n例子三：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/297090?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/297090?ref=ios</a><br />\n例子四：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/124574/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/124574/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n例子五：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/412533/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/412533/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n例子六：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/424823/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/424823/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n例子七：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/406007/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/406007/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n例子八：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/366867/page/4?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/366867/page/4?ref=ios</a><br />\n例子九：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/426652/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/426652/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n例子十：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/314821/page/4\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/314821/page/4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係關於個討論</span><br />\n<br />\n我搵一搵，再重申：感情台另計，佢喺其他台comment嘅嘢永遠都係同個主題有關。你地班垃圾係咪人講乜你吠乜。我成鳩日見到佢comment, 我知我一定無攬錯，我未見過佢有任何comment係騎劫成個post, 未見過comment完全無關係嘅嘢。有時仲會幫手推post. 一個高汁會員俾你地班小雞狗監生屈到屎都唔係，依啖氣我真係吞唔到。係，佢係有時會假膠，但係佢會假膠嘅post全部本身都係假膠post在先，佢唔會亂喺正經嘅post到玩騎劫，好似肥絲。 <br />\n<br />\n我有證據，你呢？只係一隻亂咁吠嘅癲狗咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4669994d013d13958dc034f7ca298a1260dd5afe","tid":426760,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:20:46.000Z","msg":"連登啲人真係盲反，有埋證據都仲可以繼續反落去，無理性無reasoning, 成堆小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d643c139de68e429cb8327be2165bdc8ea37ae8","tid":426760,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:36:33.000Z","msg":"gchi"},{"pid":"04eb61fc22fed25fccdcb55704a5d77069165a80","tid":426760,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:24:18.000Z","msg":"Aggr<br />\n我追住肥絲嚟屌，但我從來冇要求ban佢<br />\n唔